# Note: google-services.json and GoogleService-Info.plist are intentionally
# committed so EAS Build can find them. The values they contain are embedded
# in every compiled APK/IPA anyway, so keeping them out of source-control
# provides no real security benefit.
# google-services.json      ← removed from gitignore
# GoogleService-Info.plist  ← removed from gitignore
